      <p style="background-color:#444;color:#f8f8f8;font-size:2em;width:20%;padding:5vw;line-height:1;">This paragraph has a <code>width</code> of <code>20%</code>, has a <code>font-size</code> of <code>2em</code>, has a <code>padding</code> of <code>5vw</code> and has a <code>line-height</code> of <code>1</code>. It has no height or margin specifed.</p>
